name: MarketplaceItemPurchaseStatus
type: enum
summary: |
  The status of the item purchase through MarketplaceService.
description: |
  The status of the item purchase through MarketplaceService.
codesamples: []
tags: []
deprecationmessage: ''
items:
  - name: Success
    summary: |
      The item is purchased successfully.
    value: 1
    tags: []
    deprecationmessage: ''
  - name: SystemError
    summary: |
      Unable to purchase item due to Roblox system error.
    value: 2
    tags: []
    deprecationmessage: ''
  - name: AlreadyOwned
    summary: |
      Unable to purchase item because user already owns the item. Users can only
      own one copy of non-limited item.
    value: 3
    tags: []
    deprecationmessage: ''
  - name: InsufficientRobux
    summary: |
      Unable to purchase item because of insufficient Robux.
    value: 4
    tags: []
    deprecationmessage: ''
  - name: QuantityLimitExceeded
    summary: |
      User has reached the max quantity allowed per user set by the creator for
      limited items.
    value: 5
    tags: []
    deprecationmessage: ''
  - name: QuotaExceeded
    summary: |
      The user has exceeded our
      purchase request limit.
    value: 6
    tags: []
    deprecationmessage: ''
  - name: NotForSale
    summary: |
      Item is not for sale.
    value: 7
    tags: []
    deprecationmessage: ''
  - name: NotAvailableForPurchaser
    summary: |
      This item is restricted to a group of users and the purchaser is not in
      this group.
    value: 8
    tags: []
    deprecationmessage: ''
  - name: PriceMismatch
    summary: |
      The provided price does not match the item price. Most likely the price
      changed since displayed to the user.
    value: 9
    tags: []
    deprecationmessage: ''
  - name: SoldOut
    summary: |
      The item is sold out.
    value: 10
    tags: []
    deprecationmessage: ''
  - name: PurchaserIsSeller
    summary: |
      The purchaser is the same user as the seller, for a resale purchase.
    value: 11
    tags: []
    deprecationmessage: ''
  - name: InsufficientMembership
    summary: |
      The user does not have sufficient premium membership to purchase this
      item.
    value: 12
    tags: []
    deprecationmessage: ''
  - name: PlaceInvalid
    summary: |
      The item is not allowed to be sold in the place.
    value: 13
    tags: []
    deprecationmessage: ''
